org.sakaiproject.news.impl

Class BasicNewsItemEnclosure

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.news.impl.BasicNewsItemEnclosure
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NewsItemEnclosure

    public class BasicNewsItemEnclosure
extends Object
implements NewsItemEnclosure

    BasicNewsItemEnclosure is default implementation of the Interface for a Sakai News message enclsoures.

    The news message enclsure has header fields (type, size) and a url of the actual enclosed file. All fields are read only.

    Author:
    Joshua Ryan joshua.ryan@asu.edu alt^i
